  "instructions": [
    "Cook fettuccine pasta according to package instructions until al dente, then set aside.",
    "In a blender, combine palm vinegar, soy sauce, olive oil, garlic, ginger, and black pepper. Blend until smooth.",
    "Add the blended mixture to a large mason jar and stir in the sardines.",
    "Add the cooked fettuccine pasta to the mason jar and toss until well combined.",
    "Season with salt to taste, then garnish with chopped scallions and kalamansi or lime wedges.",
    "Serve immediately and enjoy!"
